    <http://schema.org/description> "Hello! Be aware, design is in flow, not fixed - while the placement of things are pretty fixed, colors and buttons might still change. TODO: split the cards (profile, bio, resume...) accordingly. make them editable when logged in bypass the usage of RDF forms, for editing profile (which also means we do not need to change contacts-pane now). take the colors from figma and add them to the profile. Work locally for now by updating the css vars in the dev css file. (for now we also work locally to override solid-ui css). keep accessibility features we shall also add mobile features - will mostly done through CSS and the new pane-registry interface. We have a mobile design for profile too.";
